&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Anticipated Posting Close Date*: &lt;/strong&gt;July 14, 2026&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;*Job posting may close early due to the volume of applicants.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Architect, Office of the CTO&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Fastly helps people stay better connected with the things they love. We’re building a more trustworthy, performant, and secure internet, and we’re looking for a deeply technical, highly collaborative Architect to help shape the future of our platform.&lt;/p&gt;
